Build ID: 20110928134238

Steps to reproduce:

Tried to print a news story from MSNBC.  The url is:
http://www.msnbc.msn.com/id/45346041/ns/us_news-life/#.TsZ9VHLP605


Actual results:

The "video", "discuss", and "related" content is pushed into the headline area, obscuring the headline.  This happens in IE as well, and it happens with my PDF printer and with my hard copy printer.


Expected results:

It should have printed as shown.

(BTW, just in case you actually read the story, the original was retracted by Reuters.  The child poverty rate is 1 in 5, not 1 in 3.)
